  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Whole body cryotherpy (WBC) efficacy assesment</measure>
    <time_frame>15 days</time_frame>
    <description>assess WBC efficacy on disease activity with Bath Ankylosing Spondylitis Activity Index improvement between baseline and week 2 in patients with active axial spondyloarthritis. a difference of 20 points on BASDAI scale is expected between the experimental arm and the placebo is expected</description>
