  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients suffering from axial spondyloarthritis diagnosed according to ASAS criteria,
             with sacroiliitis on X-rays or MRI, with active disease (BASDAI &gt; 4/10) despite a
             stable treatment will be included.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  contra indication to cooling,

          -  previous WBC treatment,

          -  no social security cover
      </textblock>
